hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Will I be paid weekly or monthly? medrol dose pack anxiety Helen Thomas never would have tweeted such a thing. She might have rolled her eyes and made a comment back. And it's because Thomas was a professional reporter in the most critical meaning of the phrase. She reported. She asked direct questions without caring if they offended the subject of her inquiry, but she didn't ask questions whose sole purpose was to embarrass the subject of her inquiry. She was a newswoman, pure and simple. And we are all the worse for losing her.
